---
title: Hoisin Pork Stir Fry  with Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: Everyone loves a stir-fry so we’ve packed this one full of a bounty of flavours and hidden treasures. Juicy pork mince has been partnered with hoisin sauce for a match made in heaven, along with stir-fried veggies and fluffy rice. Add a sprinkling of
crispy shallots for extra crunch!
